+- `tsconfig.json`, `.eslintrc.cjs`, `vitest.config.ts` -- Build/test config
 
 ## Validation
 
 ```bash
 npm run build   # TypeScript compilation must succeed
 npm run lint    # ESLint must pass
-npm test        # All 55 tests must pass
+npm test        # Tests must pass
 ```
